<section class="igorot">
  <div class="igorot-intro general-padding">
    <h2>Igorot</h2>
    <p>The Igorot, sometimes called Cordilleran, is a conglomeration of six groups living in the Cordilleras mountains of Luzon. They are rice-terrace farmers and hunter-gatherers. Some were also head-hunters. The Igorot often throws communal feasts
      during special occasions. Though classified as a homogenous group by the Filipino government, they don't consider themselves as one people.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="igorotCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#igorotCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#igorotCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#igorotCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
